Okweyongera okw'amaanyi mu bulwadde bwa coronavirus (COVID-19) mu Bulaaya/Ekifo ky'Eby'enfuna ekya Bulaaya ne Bungereza, okuva nga 1 Jjanwali okutuuka nga 15 Maaki 2020
Obulwadde bwa coronavirus (COVID-19) bulaga enkola y'emu mu mawanga ga European Union/European Economic Area ne United Kingdom nga kino kikakasa nti, wadde nga mu biseera eby'enjawulo okusinziira ku ggwanga, ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kikulaakulana mu bwangu mu mawanga gonna.
Okusinziira ku by'obudde okuva mu Italy, amawanga, amalwaliro n'ebizimbe ebirongoosa birina okwongera okwetegekera omuwendo gw'abalwadde abalina COVID-19 abagenda okwetaaga obujjanjabi, naddala obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi.
Nga 31 December 2019, ekibinja ky'abalwadde b'obulwadde bw'ensusu obutasobose kyalagibwa mu Wuhan, Hubei Province, China.
Nga 9 January 2020, ekitongole kya China eky'okulabirira n'okutangira endwadde kyawa amawulire nti ekirwadde kino kye kivudde mu coronavirus empya kati eyitibwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Okuva olwo, obulwadde obuva ku bulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 bubadde buyitibwa obulwadde bwa coronavirus (COVID-19).
Obujulizi obutuuse ku lunaku luno bulaga nti abantu nga 80% abalina COVID-19 balina obulwadde obutonotono, kwe kugamba, obulwadde bw'emyoyo nga bulina oba nga tebirina pulmonya, era abasinga obungi ku bano bawona.
Mu bitundu ebikumi na bina mu 14, COVID-19 yeeyongerayo mu bulwadde obw'amaanyi obwetaagisa okudda mu ddwaliro ate ebitundu ebisigadde ebikumi na mukaaga mu mukaaga bifuna obulwadde obw'amaanyi obwetaagisa okulabirirwa ennyo.
Okufa kw'abalwadde abaddusiddwa mu malwaliro olw'ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kuli ku 4%.
Mu kunoonyereza kuno, twekenneenya enkulaakulana y'obubonero bw'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga lya Bulaaya/Ekifo ky'Eby'enfuna ekya Bulaaya (EU/EEA) ne Bungereza (UK) era ne tubigeraageranya ku bya ssaza lya Hubei, mu China.
Era tugeraageranya omuwendo gw'abandu abali mu kkoyiru mu nsi za EU/EEA ne Bungereza n'ogwa Italy wakati wa 31 January ne 15 March 2020.
Embeera za COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne Bungereza
Oluvannyuma lw'ekika kya China, COVID-19 yayongera okusaasaana mu bitundu ebirala era embeera y'ekirwadde kya COVID-19 mu nsi yonna mu kiseera kino egoberera eya ggwanga lino.
Nga 11 March 2020, Director General w'ekitongole ky'ensi yonna eky'ebyobulamu (WHO) yalangirira nti COVID-19 kye kizibu ekiruma abantu.
Mu magazini ya Eurosurveillance 2020 eya Maaki 5, Spiteri n'abalala baategeezezza ku bantu abaasooka mu Bulaaya okukakasibwa nti balina COVID-19 okusinziira ku ntegeka y'ekitundu kya WHO.
Mu EU/EEA, abantu basatu abaasooka okukakasibwa nga baakafuna obulwadde buno baalabikibwa nga 24 January 2020 mu bantu abaava e Wuhan, mu ssaza lya Hubei, mu China.
Nga 15 March 2020, abantu abali mu kkooti baalabikiddwa nga balina COVID-19 mu nsi 30 ez'omu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza (UK), nga wakati wa 31 December 2019 n'olunaku olwo mw'otwalidde, abantu 39,768 be baalabikiddwa nga balina COVID-19 era nga 1,727 be baafa, nga 17,750 be baalabikiddwa nga balina COVID-19 ate 1,441 be baafa mu Italy yokka.
Okufuna omuwendo gw'abanduuse COVID-19 n'obubonero bw'abanduuse
Mu European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC), omuwendo gw'abantu abaakafuna COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga mu nsi yonna, ogufuna okuva mu nsi ezitali zimu nga Minisitule y'ebyobulamu, ab'obuyinza mu by'obulamu mu ggwanga ne mu bitundu ne mu WHO, gukuzibwa buli lunaku ku ssaawa 8:00 ez'oku makya.
Ebikwata ku COVID-19 byakozesebwa okulambula embeera mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza, n'okugeraageranya n'ebyo ebiri mu Italy.
Ng'ekitegeeza obuzibu bw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abakola, twasalawo obuzibu bw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 obwa nnaku 14, nga bwe tulabye engeri COVID-19 gye yatambulamu mu buli ggwanga lya EU/EEA ne Bungereza, wakati wa 1 January ne 15 March 2020.
Era twalaga omuwendo gw'abantu abaabadde bakwatibwa buli ggwanga nga 15 March 2020 ku ssaawa 8:00 ez'oku makya nga tugeraageranya n'ogwa Italy mu kiseera kya 31 January-15 March 2020.
Enkulaakulana ya COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne Bungereza
Enkulaakulana mu nnaku 14 ez'obubonero bw'abandu aba COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne Bungereza mu bujjuvu yakoppa eya Hubei Province (China) (Ekifaananyi 1).
Mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza mu bujjuvu, omuwendo gw'abantu abaakafuna COVID-19 gwatandika okweyongera nga 21 Febwali ne gukula nnyo nga 28 Febwali 2020 (Ekyongerezeddwako).
Kino kyakulemberwa nnyo okwongera okangu mu muwendo gw'abantu abaalabikiddwa okuva mu Italy, naye amawanga amalala gonna aga EU/EEA ne Bungereza gaalaga enkulaakulana y'omuwendo gw'abantu abaakafuna COVID-19 (Ekyongerezeddwako).
Ekifaananyi 2 kiraga omuwendo gw'abantu abaakafuna COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne Bungereza bw'ogugeraageranya ku Italy mu 31 January-15 March 2020.
Kiggumiza nti nga 15 March ku ssaawa 8:00 ez'oku makya, ensi 15 endala za EU/EEA n'eggwanga lya Bungereza zaali zamala dda okulangirira omuwendo gw'abanduusizza ku bulwadde ogugeraageranyizibwa n'ogwa Italy wiiki 3 zokka emabega oba nga tezinnaba.
Ebivudde mu kunoonyereza kwaffe biraga nti omuwendo gw'abantu abaalabikiddwa nga balina COVID-19 gweyongedde nnyo mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza.
Enkola eziri mu kuddamu okusaasaana kw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 ziraga nti ekirwadde kino kigenda mu maaso mu sipiidi y'emu mu nsi zonna.
Kino kiri bwe kityo wadde nga amawanga gali mu mitendera egy'enjawulo, enjawulo mu by'okuddamu mu by'obulamu mu ggwanga, era nga wayinza okubaawo enjawulo mu ngeri gye bategeeramu abalwadde n'enkola ez'enjawulo ez'okulonda abalwadde abasaanidde okukeberebwa okukakasa nti balina COVID-19, omuli n'okwekebejja.
Mu ntandikwa ya March 2020, abasawo mu bitundu bya Italy ebikoseddwa baalaze embeera nga 10% ku balwadde abalina COVID-19 beetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi era ebikozesebwa mu mawulire byalaga nti amalwaliro ne ebitongole ebikuuma obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi mu bitundu bino byali biweddeko obusobozi bwabyo.
Ebikwata ku kukkiriza abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu ddwaliro ne/oba mu kitongole ekirabirira ennyo mu kiseera kino biriko ku mutendera gwa EU/EEA ku 6% ne 1% byokka, okusinziira ku byafaayo (ebiri mu bitabo tebiraga).
Kyokka, birina okukuŋŋaanyizibwa mu ngeri entegeke obulungi okusobola okwongera ku by'okwetegereza ebikolebwa mu kiseera kino, ebissa essira ku muwendo gw'abantu abaalabikiddwa n'omuwendo gw'abafudde.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu 201011 kwalaga enjawulo ya maanyi mu busige obuli mu ddwaliro ery'obulabe n'obulabe obw'omuddiriŋŋanwa mu Bulaaya, okuva ku 29.2 mu Bugirimaani okutuuka ku 4.2 ku buli bantu 100,000 mu Portugal.
Kino kitegeeza nti ensi ziyinza okuba n'ensimbi ezisinga oba ezisinga obutono okusinga Italy (12,5 emitanda gy'okulabirira ennyo n'okulabirira wakati buli 100,000 mu 2010).
Ebika by'okulaga engeri y'okulabirira obulwadde ebikwatagana n'okutuuka ku buzibu bw'okujjanjaba, nga ku buli ggwanga lya EU/EEA ne Bungereza, obwenjawulo bw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abali mu malwaliro, nga bwe kirina akabi ak'okusukka 90% ak'okusukka obuyinza bw'ebitanda ebirongoofu, biweereddwa mu kukyusa okw'omukaaga okw'ebika bya ECDC eby'okukebera akabi ka COVID-19.
Okuva nga okutuusa kati abantu bano basangibwa mu bitundu ebimu mu nsi za EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza, era nga n'amalwaliro n'ebizimbe ebirimu obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi bitera okujjanjaba abantu ab'omu bitundu ebimu, obubaka obukwata ku bantu bano n'ebitanda ebirimu obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi bulina okuteekebwa mu Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Ebyamanyi okuva mu Italy n'ebiriwo mu nsi endala biraga nti ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kikulaakulana mu bwangu mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza.
Amawanga, amalwaliro n'ebibiina ebirongoosa eby'obulwadde bw'obutabukira birina okwetegekera embeera ey'okusaasaanya SARS-CoV-2 mu bantu n'okweyongera kw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abeetaaga obujjanjabi, naddala obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi, nga bwe kirina mu bitundu bya Italy ebikwatiddwako obulwadde buno.
Nga bwe kyalagibwa mu kunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu bbanga ttono okwakolebwa ECDC, enkola ey'amangu, ey'obutebenkevu era ey'obutagwa lubege nkulu nnyo okuteeka mu nkola okusaasaana kwa SARS-COV-2, nga kukyusa enkola y'okusiba ku kutereeza, kubanga okwongera kw'abalwadde okw'amangu ennyo okw'ebigendererwa eby'okusuubira kiyinza obutewa basalawo n'amalwaliro ebbanga erimala okutegeera, okukkiriza n'okukyusa eky'okukola nga bwe kisaanye singa tekikolebwa mu budde.
Okunoonyereza ku kabi akali mu bwangu era kulaga enkola z'obulamu obwa bulijjo ez'okuggyawo obuzibu bw'ekirwadde kino.
Waliwo akaseera akatono ak'ebiseera amawanga mwe gasobola okwongera amaanyi mu kufuga okusaanyaawo SARS-CoV-2 n'okusaanyaawo okupikirizibwa ku by'obulamu.
Kino bwe kitabaawo, kirabika nti enkola z'obujjanjabi mu nsi endala za EU/EEA zijja kufuna omuwendo omungi ogw'abalwadde abeetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi mu nnaku oba wiiki ezijja.
Ekirwadde kya Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19), ekiva ku siriimu ey'amaanyi ey'obutafu (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kikutte abantu abasukka mu 3,000 era kisobodde okukwata abantu abasukka mu 80,000 mu China n'ebitundu ebirala mu nsi, ekireeseewo akatyabaga eri abantu.
Okufaananako akawuka ke ka SARS-CoV, akaaleetera abantu enkumi n'enkumi okufuna SARS mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 nayo esobola okussibwa okuva mu biwuka era ne kireeta obubonero obufaananako ng'akozesa enkola y'emu.
Kyokka, COVID-19 erina obuzibu obutonotono n'okufa okusinga SARS naye esinga okuyisa abantu era ekwata ku bantu abakaddiye okusinga abavubuka n'abasajja okusinga abakazi.
