WHO yasiimye ab'obuyinza mu China olw'okufuba okufuga n'okusiba ekirwadde kino.
WHO ekutte enjawulo wakati w'akabenje ka SARS akaaliwo mu 2002-2004, nga ab'obuyinza mu China bavunaanibwa obuteebakabe obwayita mu kuziyiza n'okukuuma obwavu, n'akabenje akaliwo kati nga gavumenti enkulu "ewadde obupapula obutayosa okwewala okutya ng'olunaku lw'omwaka omuggya terunnatuuka".
Nga 23 January, ng'addamu okusalawo kw'abakulu mu gavumenti okutongoza ekiragiro ky'entambula mu Wuhan, omubaka wa WHO Gauden Galea yagamba nti wadde "tekyali kiragiro kya WHO", naye era "kyali kikakasa nnyo obumalirivu obw'okukugira ekirwadde mu kifo we kisinga okwekeneenya" era n'akiyita "ekitabangawo mu byafaayo by'obulamu".Nga 30 January, oluvannyuma lw'okukakaatirwa nti abantu basangibwa mu bantu ebweru wa China n'okweyongera kw'omuwendo gw'abantu abaakafuna ekirwadde mu nsi endala, WHO yalangirira ekirwadde kino okuba eky'obutabanguko mu by'obulamu bw'abantu (PHEIC), ekirwadde eky'omukaaga okuva ekirwadde kino lwe kyatandika okukozesebwa mu 2009 mu bulwadde bw'enkwaso y'embizzi.
