Kino era kyavaamu okukendeera kwa 3343% mu mmotoka ez'ebigere mu butale mu March bw'ogerageranya ne February.
Abakola mu bifo eby'okuddukanyizaamu ebintu okwetooloola ensi baateekawo enkola endala, gamba ng'okwongerayo obuyonjo, okuteekawo ebikessi ebikebera ebbugumu ly'abaguzi, n'okuyimbula emikolo. Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa ekitongole ky'amawanga amagatte ekikola ku by'enfuna mu Latin America, enkola y'okweyongerayongera kw'ebyenfuna ey'ekibonyoobonyo eyinza okuleka abantu abali wakati wa bukadde 14 ne 22 mu bwavu obw'amaanyi mu Latin America okusinga bwe kyandibadde mu mbeera eyo singa tewabangawo kawumpuli.
Mu January ne February 2020, mu kiseera ekikyasinze okutabula mu Wuhan, abantu nga bukadde 5 mu China baafiirwa emirimu gyabwe.
Bangi ku bakozi ba China abagenda mu byalo kumpi obukadde 300 basangiddwa mu maka gaabwe mu bitundu by'omu byalo oba basangiddwa mu ssaza lya Hubei. Mu March 2020, Abamerika abasukka mu bukadde 10 baafiirwa emirimu gyabwe ne basaba obuyambi bwa gavumenti.
Ekirwadde kya coronavirus kiyinza okufiiriza emirimu 47 mu Amerika ate n'obutaba na mirimu kiyinza okutuuka ku 32%, okusinziira ku bukebera bwa Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis. Okusiba mu Buyindi kuleese obukadde n'obukadde bw'abakozi ab'omu Buyindi abagenda mu nsi endala (abaweebwa empeera ya buli lunaku) nga tebalina mirimu. Okunoonyereza okuva mu Angus Reid Institute kwazuula nti 44% ku maka ga Canada gafunye obutaba na mirimu. Abakozi nga 900,000 baafiirwa emirimu gyabwe mu Spain okuva lwe kyatandika okukugirwa mu makkati ga Maaki 2020.
Mu kitundu eky'okubiri eky'omwezi gwa Maaki, abakozi ba France obukadde 4 beeyambisa ensimbi z'obutaba na mulimu ez'akaseera obuseera ate abakozi ba Bungereza obukadde 1 beeyambisa enteekateeka y'obuyambi.
