b' Enzamu ey'okufuula angiotensin 2 (ACE2) enzimu ekwatagana n'ebweru w'ebitundu by'omubiri (cell membranes) mu mpumi, mu misayi, mu mutima, mu buwunda, ne mu bitundu by'omubiri.
ACE2 ekomya ebikolwa bya angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) nga ekendeeza omuwendo gwa angiotensin-II era ng'eyongera Ang (((1-7) nga kino kikakasa nti eddagala eryo lijja kuyamba mu kulwanyisa endwadde z'omutima. ACE2 era likola ng'ekifo eky'okuyingira mu buwuka bwa coronaviruses ezimu.
Ensiimu ey'omuntu eyitibwa hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 y'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika ky'ekika.
Ebikwaso bya ACE2 birimu ekitundu kya N-terminal peptidase M2 ne C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 ye protein ya membrane type I ey'omugongo oguyita omulundi gumu, nga ekitundu kyayo ekikolera ku enzyme kibeera ku mutendera gwa ssere mu biwundu ne mu bitundu ebirala.
Ekitundu ekyawukana ku ssere lya ACE2 kifuluma mu kitundu ekya transmembrane nga kiyitibwa enzyme endala eyitibwa sheddase, era protein egguka eggibwa mu musaayi era oluvannyuma n'eggibwa mu musaayi.
ACE2 eri mu bitundu ebisinga obungi eby'omubiri: ACE2 ekwatagana n'enkula y'omu mubiri naddala mu bitundu by'omu bwongo eby'ekika II, enterocytes ez'omu bulago obutonotono, obutoffaali bw'omusaayi n'obw'omusaayi n'obutoffaali bw'omusaayi omutono mu bitundu ebisinga obungi eby'omubiri.
ACE2 mRNA nayo ejjudde mu cortex, striatum, hypothalamus, ne brainstem.
Omulimu omukulu ogwa ACE2 kwe kukola ng'omutego gw'omugaso gwa ACE.
ACE ekwata angiotensin I mu angiotensin II ey'omutawaana.
ACE2 mu ngeri ye, ekwata carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine okuva mu angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) era n'egibikka mu angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 esobola n'okusiba ebika ebirala nga [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, ne ghrelin.
ACE2 era erongoosa ekidduka kya membrane ekya SLC6A19 era ekwataganyizibwa n'obulwadde bwa Hartnup.
Ng'obutoffaali obutuusa ku mubiri, ACE2 ye nsonga enkulu ey'okuyingira mu buwuka bwa coronaviruses ezimu, omuli HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus etera okuleeta SARS); ne SARS-CoV-2 (virus etera okuleeta COVID-19).
Ekisingawo n'obwangu, okukwatagana kwa protein ya spike S1 eya SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV2 ku enzyme ya ACE2 ku bbanga ly'ebisenge kuleeta endosytosis n'okusengula kwa virus ne enzyme mu endosomes eziri munda mu bisenge.
Enkola eno ey'okuyingira era yeetaagisa S protein okusooka okuteekebwa mu mubiri nga serine protease TMPRSS2, ekirwadde ekiruma ekirwadde kino ekiragibwa nga kirina obuyinza okujjanjaba. Kino kireetedde abamu okulowooza nti okukendeeza ku mutindo gwa ACE2 mu butoffaali, kiyinza okuyamba mu kulwanyisa obulwadde.
Kyokka, ebibiina by'obuyigirize n'ebitongole ebirongoosa biwadde amagezi okweyongera okujjanjaba n'abazigu ba ACE n'aba ARB.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku July 11, 2012, kwalaga nti "okukozesa obuwuka obulemesa ACE kwaviirako omuntu okufuna obulwadde bw'ensusu ez'obutwa mu bitundu 34 ku buli kikumi bw'obageraageranya ku bantu abalala. "
Ate era, "akabi k'obulwadde bw'ensusu kaaliko n'akato mu balwadde abajjanjabibwa n'abaziyiza ACE abaalina akabi k'obulwadde bw'ensusu, naddala abo abaalina obulwadde bw'omusaayi n'obutaba na mutima.
Okukozesa abaziyiza ACE era kwavvuunulwa n'okusaanyaawo okufa kw'abantu abafa olw'obulwadde bw'ensusu, wadde nga ebivudde mu kunoonyereza okwo byali bitono nnyo okusinga eby'obulabe bw'obulwadde bw'ensusu".
Ekirungo kya ACE2 eky'abantu eky'okuzzaawo (rhACE2) kigambibwa okuba eddagala eriggya ku bulwadde bw'omu bwongo obw'amaanyi, era kirabika kyongera ku bulwadde bw'omusaayi n'obutaba na ssukaali mu biwuka mu biwalaalo ebirina obulwadde bw'obutaba na ssukaali.
Ekiseera eky'okusaasaana kwa rhACE2 mu bantu kiri ssaawa nga 10 era ekitundu ky'omugaso kikula mu ddakiika 30 ng'oggyeko ekiseera eky'omugaso (ekiseera) eky'essaawa 24.
Ebimu ku by'okuzuula biraga nti rhACE2 eyinza okuba eddagala erisuubizo eri abo abalina obutabaganya ku buzibu bw'enteekateeka ya renin-angiotensin (RAS inhibitors) oba mu ndwadde mweyongedde angiotensin II.
b'Ebikwatagana ne COVID-19 bye bikwatagana ne programu ez'essimu ezikoleddwa okuyamba mu kukwata abantu nga bwe bwayita mu bulwadde bwa coronavirus 2019-20, kwe kugamba, enkola ey'okumanya abantu ("abaakwatagana") abayinza okuba nga baakafuna obuzibu n'omuntu alina obulwadde.
Enkola nnyingi zaakolebwa oba ne ziteekebwateekebwa, nga zirina obuwagizi bwa gavumenti mu bitundu ebimu n'obwenkanya.
Enkola ezitali zimu ez'okuzimba app ez'okukebera abantu ze zikoleddwa.
Okwebuuza ku by'obwannannyini kwogeddwa, naddala ku nkola ezisinziira ku kukwata ekifo eky'obwannannyini eky'abakozesa app.
Ebirala ebitajja kumuyingiza nnyo mu bantu kwe kukozesa Bluetooth okuwandiika amannya g'omuntu ng'ali kumpi n'essimu endala.
Nga 10 April 2020, Google ne Apple baalangirira nti bagenda kwenyigira mu nkola ez'okuwagira app za Bluetooth nga zitambulira mu nkola zaabwe ez'okusimba eza Android ne iOS.
Mu China, gavumenti ya China, nga ekola ne Alipay, etaddewo app esobozesa abantu okukebera oba nga bafunye akakwate n'abantu abalina COVID-19.
Kikozesebwa mu bibuga eby'omu China ebisukka mu 200. Mu Singapore, app eyitibwa TraceTogether ekozesebwa.
App eno yakolerwa ekibiina kya IT ekya mu kitundu, era yafulumizibwa nga open source era ejja kuweebwa gavumenti. Macedonia ow'ebukiikakkono yatandikawo "StopKorona!", app esinziira ku Bluetooth okusala amangu abantu abayinza okuba nga balina akawuka era n'okuddamu mu bwangu ab'obuyinza mu by'obulamu.
App eno yakolerwa Minisitule y'ebyempuliziganya n'ebikugu n'Eby'obulamu.
Nga 14 April 2020, app eno yali esubirwa okuweebwa akasiimo ka Google Play Store ne Apple App Store.
Nga 12 April, gavumenti yalagidde nti app ey'okunoonya abantu yali mu kutendekebwa okw'amaanyi era nti yandibaddewo mu bbanga lya wiiki ntono. App efaananako ng'eyo eteekeddwa mu pulaani mu Ireland ne mu Bufalansa ("StopCovid").
Australia ne New Zealand bbiri zisalawo ku mpapula ezesigamiziddwa ku TraceTogether app ne BlueTrace protocol eza Singapore. Russia eteekateeka okutandikawo geofencing app eri abalwadde abazuuliddwa nga balina COVID-19 ababeera mu Moscow, nga kigendereddwamu okukakasa nti tebava waka.
Ross Anderson, profesa mu by'obukuumi ku yunivasite y'e Cambridge, yalaga ebizibu bingi ebiyinza okubaawo mu nkola ezikozesa apps, omuli n'obubaka obulimba n'obutaba na mugaso singa app eyo ekozesebwa abantu batono nnyo.
Ng'eyogera ku kweraliikirira ku kubunyisa "coronavirus" apps ez'obulimba oba ez'akabi, Apple yassaawo ekkomo ku ngeri y'ebitongole ezisobola okugatta apps ezikwata ku coronavirus mu App Store, nga zikugira ebitongole "ebikwatiddwa" oba ebirina ekitiibwa.
Google ne Amazon zikozesezza endagiriro ez'engeri y'emu.
Abalwanirira eby'obwannannyini baalaze okweraliikirira kwabwe ku buzibu obuva mu kukwata abantu nga bakozesa apps za coronavirus, naddala ku nsonga y'okuba nti ebyuma ebikuuma abantu ebikoleddwa okulwanyisa ekirwadde kya coronavirus bijja kuggibwawo ng'obulabe bumaze okuggwaawo.
Amnesty International n'ebibiina ebirala ebisoba mu 100 byafulumya ekiteeso nga basaba okukugira okulondoola okw'engeri eno.
Ebibiina byalangiridde embeera munaana ku pulojekiti za gavumenti:
okwetegereza kwandibadde "kulina okuba okw'amateeka, okwetaagisa era okw'omuganyulo";
okwetoloola n'okukuuma byandyeyongedde nga birimu ebiragiro ebiragira nti obudde buwedde;
Enkola y'okukozesa ebikonde erina okukoma ku COVID-19;
Obukuumi bw'obubaka n'obuteeyitibwa bikwata ku bantu b'obwannannyini, era birina okukuumibwa era birina okulagibwa nti birina okukuumibwa okusinziira ku bujulizi;
okwetegereza mu ngeri ey'obuntu kwandyewaze okwongera ku kusosola n'okuteekebwa ku mabbali;
Okwawulawo kwonna kw'ebikwata ku bantu abalala kwanditeekeddwa okussibwa mu mateeka;
wandibaddewo obukuumi ku bukyamu n'eddembe ly'abantu okuddamu obuzibu;
"okwenyigira mu ngeri ey'amakulu" kw'abo bonna "abaalina ensonga" kwandibadde kwetaagisa, omuli abakugu mu by'obulamu mu bantu n'ebibinja ebiremereddwa. Akakiiko ka German Chaos Computer Club (CCC) ne Reporters Without Borders (Reporter ohne Grenzen) (RSF) nabo baaleeta ebirondoola.
Enteekateeka eya Google/Apple eteekateeka okugonjoola ekizibu ky'okukebera okw'olubeerera nga baggyamu enkola y'okunoonya mu nkola zaabwe ez'okukozesa ebyuma bwe kitaba nga kyetaagisa.
Ensi ezimu zaakozesa obukodyo bw'okuteeka abantu ku mutimbagano mu kifo ky'okuteeka apps, ne kiba nti tekikyali kyetaagisa kukwata app n'okweggyako okuteeka abantu ku mutimbagano.
Mu Isiraeri, okulondoola okusinziira ku mutimbagano kwaweebwa olukusa.
Ensalawo ez'oku mutimbagano ezirina okuyingira mu bikwata ku kifo ekitaliiko biwandiiko birina ebizibu eby'amaanyi eby'obukuumi.
Kyokka, si buli nkola erina serveri za kkampuni ez'enjawulo ezirina okufunako obubaka ku kifo omuntu gy'alimu; enteekateeka ez'enjawulo ezikuuma eby'obwannannyini zikoleddwa nga zikozesa serveri za kkampuni ez'enjawulo okuwuliziganya (laba akatundu akali wansi).
Mu South Korea, enkola etesigamiziddwa ku mpapula yakozesebwa okukola okuzuula abantu.
Mu kifo ky'okukozesa app ey'enjawulo, enkola yakuŋŋaanya obubaka obuva mu nsibuko ez'enjawulo omuli obubaka obuva ku byuma ebikuba essimu n'obw'ebikukwatako, era n'ebikuba awamu ne bifulumya obubaka okuyita mu bubaka obuba bubadde buweereddwa abantu abayinza okuba nga balina obulwadde.
Ng'oggyeko okukozesa obubaka buno okulabula abantu abayinza okujja mu bantu, gavumenti era erese obubaka obukwata ku kifo omuntu gy'ali, ekintu ekikkirizibwa olw'enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi ezaakolebwa mu mateeka agakwata ku kyama ky'obuntu oluvannyuma lw'ekirwadde kya MERS mu nsi eyo.
Amawulire gano gasangibwa eri abantu bonna okuyita mu mpapula ezitali zimu ne ku mikutu gya Intaneeti. Ensi omuli ne Bugirimaani zirowooza ku kukozesa enkola eziri mu kibiina n'ezikuuma eby'obwannannyini.
Nga 6 April 2020, ebinnyonnyola tebyali byafulumizibwa.
Okukebera abantu nga bw'obadde weegomba, kye kigambo ekitegekeddwa obulungi, nga waliwo ebitabo bingi ebikebera eby'ebyafaayo ebikyava mu 2013. Nga 7 April 2020, ebibinja by'abakugu ebisukka mu kkumi byali bikola ku by'okuddamu ebikwasa obukuumi, gamba ng'okukozesa Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) okuwandiika obudde bw'omukozesa bw'ali okumpi ne ssimu endala.
