Obujjanjabi obw'okugezesa okuva mu nkola zino zonna bujja kuba bwa kugezesebwa ku bikwata ku bukuumi n'obuyambi. Nga 16 March 2020, okugezesebwa okusooka okw'ekirwadde ky'obutaba na bulwadde kwatandika n'abantu bana abeewaayo kyeyagalire mu Seattle.
Ekirwadde kino kirimu code y'ekika ekirwadde ekirwadde ekirwadde. Okweyongerayongera kw'ebirwadde ebirwanyisa omubiri kwogerwako ng'ekizibu ekirimu okuteekateeka ekirwadde kya SARS-COV-2, naye kino kikontana.
Waliwo okusoba mu 300 ebigezo ebikolebwa mu April 2020.
Okugezesebwa musanvu kwali kukebera obujjanjabi obwa malaliya obwali bukakasibwa, nga muno mwe mwali n'okunoonyereza okuna ku hydroxychloroquine oba chloroquine.
Eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka akajjanjabibwa likola ekisinga obungi mu kunoonyereza kw'Abakiina, nga mu nsi ezimu kuliko ebigezo bya mirundi omwenda eby'omulundi ogw'okusatu ku remdesivir ebinaalagibwa ku nkomerero ya April.
Okusooka okunoonyereza ku by'okulwanyisa bya COVID-19 n'ebirwadde ebirimu byali mu kifo kyabyo, nga April 2020. Ebirwadde ebirwanyisa akawuka kano ebiriko nga bisomebwa okujjanjaba COVID-19, omuli remdesivir, chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir ne lopinavir/ritonavir nga bizingiramu interferon beta.
Waliwo obujulizi obwesigamiziddwa ku ngeri remdesivir gye yakolamu nga Maaki 2020.
Obulungi bw'omusaayi bweyoleka mu balwadde abajjanjabibwa remdesivir eyakozesebwanga mu ngeri ey'ekisa.
Okukebera mu ddagala mu kitundu III kukoleddwa mu Amerika, China ne Italy. Chloroquine, eyali ekozesebwa eddagala ly'omusujja, yakeberebwa mu China mu February 2020, nga n'ebyavudde mu kunoonyereza byasooka.
Kyokka, waliwo okusaba okw'okukebera kunoonyereza.
