Kyokka, ekitongole kya Wuhan Institute of Virology, wadde nga kikubiriza eddagala lya gramu emu buli lunaku, kiraga nti emirundi ebiri lya kabi nnyo era lisobola okutaataaganya obulamu bw'omuntu.
Nga 28 March 2020, FDA yafulumya ekiragiro eky'okukozesa mu bwangu hydroxychloroquine ne chloroquine okusinziira ku ddwaaliro ly'abasawo abalwanyisa abantu abalina COVID-19. Enkola y'Olukusa lwa China ey'omulundi ogw'omusanvu erabamu interferon, ribavirin oba umifenovir ezikozesebwa okulwanyisa COVID-19.
Ebisooka biraga nti eddagala eddene ery'ekika kya ribavirin lyetaagisa okuziyiza SARS-CoV-2 mu in vitro.
Nitazoxanide asabiddwa okwongera okunoonyereza mu mulamu oluvannyuma lw'okulaga nti SARS-CoV-2 ekkaanya ak'ebitooke tekyakola bulungi. Okunoonyereza kulaga nti okusookera ddala, ekika ky'obutonde obwa protini ekikubiddwa mu mulamu gwa protini ey'omubiri oguyita mu mulamu gwa protini ey'omubiri oguyita mu mulamu gwa protini eyitibwa transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) kikulu nnyo mu kuyingira SARS-CoV-2 okuyita mu kukwatagana n'omulwadde ACE2.
Okunoonyereza ku chlorokini ne hydroxychloroquine nga ziriko azithromycin oba nga terina, kulina obunafu bungi obwalemesa abasawo okutandika okuzijanjaba nga tebanneeyongera kuyiga. Oseltamivir teziziyiza SARS-CoV-2 mu by'obutonde era tezirina kifo kye zimanyi mu kujjanjaba COVID-19.
Embuyaga ya cytokine esobola okuba obuzibu mu biseera eby'oluvannyuma eby'ekirwadde kya COVID-19 eky'amaanyi.
Waliwo obujulizi nti hydroxychloroquine eyinza okuba n'obuyambi obwewala ekirwadde kya cytokine. Tocilizumab yagiyingizibwa mu biragiro by'obujjanjabi okuva mu kakiiko ka China aka National Health Commission oluvannyuma lw'okumala okunoonyereza okutono.
Ekirwadde kino kikyali mu ddaala lya 2 mu Italy nga tekibadde kya randomized mu ggwanga oluvannyuma lw'okulaga nti kirina obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Nga bwekwatagana n'okwekebejja omusaayi gwa serum ferritin okwekebera embuyaga z'ebitonde, kigenda kulwanyisa embeera ng'ezo, ezirowoozebwa okuba nga ze ziviirako okufa mu bantu abamu abakoseddwa.
Ekirwadde ekirwanyisa interleukin-6 ekikkirizibwa ekitongole kya FDA okusinziira ku kunoonyereza ku nsonga ez'edda mu 2017 okujjanjaba obulwadde bwa steroid refractory cytokine release syndrome obwaliwo olw'ensonga endala, CAR T cell therapy.
Okutuusa kati, tewali bujulizi bwa randomized, obuli ku mukono nti tocilizumab y'eddagala eriganyula CRS.
Okuyisa obuwuka obunafu n'obw'omukka obuvudde mu by'omubiri by'abo abawonye COVID-19 eri abantu ababa babwetaaga, kunoonyerezaako ng'engeri etakwatagana na ddagala ly'obutabaako bujjanjabi.
Enkola eno yageragezebwa ku SARS nga terina bivaamu.
Okwewala ekirwadde kye kiragiro ekisuubirwa ekikola nga antibody therapy esobola okuyimirizaawo obukuumi ku SARS-CoV-2.
Kyokka, enkola endala, gamba ng'obutaba na buwuka mu nsiko n'obutaba na buwuka, n'obutaba na buwuka, biyinza okuba nga biyinza okubaawo.
Engeri endala ez'okujjanjaba obulwadde obuyitibwa antibody, gamba ng'okukozesa obulwadde obuyitibwa monoclonal antibodies, zikulaakulanyizibwa.
Okukola serum ey'okuwona, ekirimu ekitundu eky'omusaayi okuva mu balwadde abawonye era ekirimu obulwadde obuwakanya akawuka kano, kisobola okwongerwako okusobola okusaasaanya amangu.
